@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Flight Control Operator" as FCO
participant ":System" as System
participant ":Report Generation Thread" as ReportThread
participant ":Shared Memory" as SharedMemory
participant ":Final Simulation Report" as Report
participant ":Report File" as ReportFile

activate FCO

FCO -> System : Requests final simulation report

activate System
System --> System : Check if FCO is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate selected simulation
System --> System : Check if simulation has concluded

alt simulation has concluded

    System -> ReportThread : Request final report generation

    activate ReportThread

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read total number of flights
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Total number of flights
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read individual flight execution statuses
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Flight execution statuses
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read safety violation events
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Violations with timestamps,\npositions and velocity vectors
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read final validation result
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Pass/fail validation result
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> Report : Compile comprehensive final report
    activate Report
    Report --> ReportThread : Final report compiled
    deactivate Report

    ReportThread -> ReportFile : Save complete report to file
    activate ReportFile
    ReportFile --> ReportThread : Report file saved
    deactivate ReportFile

    ReportThread --> System : Final report file reference
    deactivate ReportThread

    System --> FCO : Display final report generated message

else simulation has not concluded

    System --> FCO : Display report unavailable until simulation concludes

else report generation or storage fails

    System --> FCO : Display report generation/storage error

end

deactivate System
deactivate FCO

@enduml